name: FORCE3
description: This is a TAS Professional 3.0 command here for compatibility. The preferred TAS Professional 5.1 command is FORCE.

parameters.name: Y/N
parameters.description: Y/N - Required - If this option is Y the program will ignore any windows when displaying information to the screen. To return to normal mode the option would be Y.

comments: This is the equivalent of the TAS Professional 3.0 command Print Outside Window.
